'''艾朗·麥連'''（{{lang-en|'''Aaron McLean'''}}，{{bd|1983年|5月25日|catidx=McLean, Aaron}}）出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[大伦敦|大伦敦]][[哈默史密斯-富勒姆區|哈默史密斯-富勒姆區]]的[[哈默史密斯|哈默史密斯]]，是一名[[足球員|足球員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，出身[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|奧連特]]青訓系統，其後在非聯賽球會打滾，直到加盟[[彼得伯勒联足球俱乐部|彼德堡]]才成名，現時效力[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[布拉德福德城足球俱乐部|巴拉福特]]。

== 生平 ==
=== 奧連特 ===
麥連出身[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|奧連特]]青訓系統，於1999年12月8日首次代表一隊在[[英格蘭聯賽錦標|英格蘭聯賽錦標]]對[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]下半場後補上陣。於1999/2000年球季末再獲3次在[[英格蘭足球聯賽|聯賽]]後補登場的機會。2000/01年球季年僅17歲的麥連雖然只有兩次出賽機會，但2001年3月6日聯賽作客對[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]首次以正選身份上陣；而3月17日聯賽作客對[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|梳士貝利]]，下半場後補上陣頂入為球隊扳平1-1<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/1224380.stm |title=Shrewsbury 1-1 L Orient |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-03-17 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307043251/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/1224380.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2001/02年球季麥連獲得較多出場機會，雖然大部份是後補身份，在31次上陣射入兩球，於2002年4月30日獲一年新約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leyton_orient/1959646.stm |title=New deal for McLean |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-04-30 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307195034/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leyton_orient/1959646.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2002/03年球季初被外借到[[格雷斯竞技足球俱乐部|格雷斯]]汲取上陣機會，但返回奧連特後仍未能在一隊掙得正選席位，更被通知在季後將不獲新約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leyton_orient/2865393.stm |title=McLean to exit Orient |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-03-19 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307084403/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leyton_orient/2865393.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

=== 艾迪索特 ===
2003年7月3日加盟新升[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|議會全國聯賽]]的[[艾迪索特镇足球俱乐部|艾迪索特]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aldershot/3041282.stm |title=Aldershot sign duo |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-07-03 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307071636/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aldershot/3041282.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。麥連在艾迪索特表現出色，更獲徵召加入由23歲以下半職業球員組成的[[英格蘭足球代表丙隊|英格蘭C隊]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/3204821.stm |title=Fairclough names England squad |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-10-22 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306224311/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/3204821.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。艾迪索特在球季結束時獲得聯賽第5位，可以參加升級附加賽，準決賽兩回合累計1-1與[[靴尔福特联足球俱乐部|赫里福特聯]]踢成平手，艾迪索特在[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]以4-2獲勝晉級決賽<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/3676425.stm |title=Hereford 0-0 Aldershot |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-05-02 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310073754/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/3676425.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，5月16日決賽對[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|梳士貝利]]，麥連上半場36分鐘先拔頭籌，但梳士貝利完半場前扳平1-1，直到[[加時賽|加時]]後再沒有增添紀錄，艾迪索特在[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]以0-3敗北而失落升級機會<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/3713971.stm |title=Shrews secure promotion |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-05-16 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2017-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827215559/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_conf/3713971.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2004/05年球季[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|議會全國聯賽]]轉制為[[職業|全職業]]聯賽，麥連與球會續約一年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aldershot/3790287.stm |title=D'Sane signs Shots deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-06-09 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307134508/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aldershot/3790287.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。但麥連到季中的表現開始滑落，只有4球斬獲，更於2005年2月2日被掛牌出售<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aldershot/4228951.stm |title=Shots transfer-list three players |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-02-02 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306233043/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aldershot/4228951.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，2月11日麥連轉投[[英格蘭足球議會南部聯賽|議會南部聯賽]]（Conference South）領頭羊[[格雷斯竞技足球俱乐部|格雷斯]]，簽約兩年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aldershot/4258357.stm |title=McLean leaves Aldershot for Grays |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-02-11 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307030619/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aldershot/4258357.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

=== 格雷斯 ===
麥連在已升級到[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|議會全國聯賽]]的[[格雷斯竞技足球俱乐部|格雷斯]]初期並不順利，苦戰到2005年12月6日對[[Altrincham_F.C.|艾青洽]]（Altrincham）才射入首球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4494992.stm |title=Grays Athletic 1-1 Altrincham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-12-06 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307162445/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4494992.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但在新年過後漸入佳境，最終協助球隊在聯賽取得第3位，再一次參加升級附加賽，但在準決賽兩回合累計4-5負於[[Halifax_Town_A.F.C.|夏利法斯]]（Halifax Town）被淘汰<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4973008.stm |title=Grays 2-2 Halifax (agg 4-5) |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-05-10 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308193935/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4973008.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。但格雷斯卻成功晉級[[英格蘭足總錦標|英格蘭足總錦標]]決賽，5月14日以2-0擊敗[[Woking_F.C.|胡京]]（Woking），順利蟬聯冠軍獎盃<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4772151.stm |title=Grays turn style into substance |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-05-15 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2019-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190111204458/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4772151.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2006/07年球季麥連表現出色，開季首17場射入13球，與[[艾贝斯费特联足球俱乐部|格拉維森]]的[[查理·麥當奴|查理·麥當奴]]（Charlie MacDonald）併列射手榜榜首，並吸引[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]及[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]等高級別球會的注意<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/g/grays_athletic/6071272.stm |title=Hottest property in the Conference |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-10-20 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307112356/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/g/grays_athletic/6071272.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2006年10月31日麥連以外借身份加盟[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]]的[[彼得伯勒联足球俱乐部|彼德堡]]，如表現滿意，將會以6位數字金額正式買斷<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6103350.stm |title=Grays star McLean moves to Posh |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-10-31 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307022233/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6103350.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。麥連加盟後勇態持續，8場比賽射入5球，將彼德堡帶入升級附加賽區域及[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]第三圈<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6171667.stm |title=Alexander seeks non-league gems |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-12-12 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028154759/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6171667.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

=== 彼德堡 ===
2007年1月2日[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]重開後首日，[[彼得伯勒联足球俱乐部|彼德堡]]隨即付出15萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]將麥連正式收歸旗下，簽約三年半<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6224749.stm |title=McLean and Morgan make Posh move |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-01-02 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2007-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070116153430/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6224749.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。麥連繼續取得入球，更在2月份連續3場聯賽各入1球，但不幸在2月17日對[[马科斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|馬爾斯菲]]雖然射入一球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/6349583.stm |title=Macclesfield 2-1 Peterborough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-02-17 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308003147/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/6349583.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但完場前受傷，賽後掃瞄證實[[膝蓋|膝蓋]][[前十字韌帶|前十字韌帶]]受創，需要提早「收咧」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6408155.stm |title=Posh striker ruled out for season |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-03-01 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307021145/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6408155.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，加盟首季連同借用期合共射入10球。麥連接受[[微創手術|微創手術]]後，可望趕及在季前訓練復出<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6423469.stm |title=McLean targets pre-season return |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-03-06 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307034242/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6423469.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。4月5日彼德堡與麥連延長合約直到2011年6月才屆滿<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6528863.stm |title=McLean agrees new deal with Posh |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-04-05 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307102337/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6528863.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2007年5月25日麥連獲准全面復操<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6690835.stm |title=Striker McLean gets green light |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-25 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307080334/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6690835.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|2007/08年球季]][[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|聯賽]]開鑼日彼德堡主場3-0輕取[[罗奇代尔足球俱乐部|罗奇代尔]]，麥連復出首場即射入一球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/6931027.stm |title=Peterborough 3-0 Rochdale |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-08-11 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2020-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016234637/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/6931027.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。11月24日主場聯賽7-0大炒[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|賓福特]]，麥連個人在上半場完成[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7099934.stm |title=Peterborough 7-0 Brentford |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-11-24 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2020-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016234647/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7099934.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2008年1月15日聯賽8-2擊潰[[艾宁顿斯坦利足球俱乐部|阿克寧頓]]，麥連與隊友[[乔治·博伊德|乔治·博伊德]]各入3球，個人本季第二次食出「大三元」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7184768.stm |title=Peterborough 8-2 Accrington |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-15 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2021-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327165950/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7184768.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。到了3月中，彼德堡位處聯賽榜次席，而麥連更以25球高據英乙射手榜首位<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7305550.stm |title=Mclean wants Posh to keep focus |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-03-19 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307180320/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7305550.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。3月29日主場4-0擊敗[[林肯城足球俱乐部|林肯城]]，麥連再入兩球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7309382.stm |title=Peterborough 4-0 Lincoln |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-03-29 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307034350/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7309382.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，個人本季入球總數達到31球，其中27球在聯賽中射入，有望取得英乙金靴獎<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7322848.stm |title=Mclean targets Golden Boot award |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-01 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307174459/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7322848.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。雖然有傳聞麥連會於季後離隊，麥連表示效忠彼德堡，並稱：「我一日仍是彼德堡的球員，將不惜為球會而汗血。」（I'm a Peterborough United player and as long as I am I will sweat blood for the club）<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7361416.stm |title=Mclean committed to Peterborough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-22 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307182718/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7361416.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。4月27日麥連入選[[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|PFA]][[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]][[PFA年度最佳陣容|年度最佳陣容]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7370319.stm |title=Ronaldo named player of the year |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-27 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2019-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323131400/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7370319.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。球季結束，麥連合共射入33球，更以29個聯賽入球成為[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]]神射手，並協助彼德堡贏得聯賽亞軍及自動升級[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]席位，季後[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球會[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]希望收購麥連，彼德堡要求先付300萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，如獲升級[[英超|英超]]再加200萬英鎊<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7470950.stm |title=Wolves told to up bid for McLean |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-06-24 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307142845/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7470950.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，麥連一度提出轉會要求<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7483982.stm |title=Mclean hands in transfer request |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-01 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307175058/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7483982.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但季前返回彼德堡參加訓練<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7505667.stm |title=Ferguson unfazed by Mclean saga |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-14 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310120210/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7505667.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，並撤回轉會掛牌<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7513744.stm |title=Mclean no longer on transfer list |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-19 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307020721/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7513744.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，於7月28日簽署四年新約結束這場轉會風波<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7529632.stm |title=Mclean and Lee pen new Posh deals |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-28 |accessdate=2009-05-17 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307071622/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7529632.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

[[2008年至2009年英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|2008/09年球季]]麥連在2008年8月16日[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]第二場聯賽主場3-0擊敗母會[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|奧連特]]取得本季首個入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7551210.stm |title=Peterborough 3-0 Leyton Orient |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-16 |accessdate=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028212121/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7551210.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。9月6日主場大手交易5-4僅勝[[布里斯托流浪足球俱乐部|布里斯托流浪]]，麥連雖1射入一球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7588621.stm |title=Peterborough 5-4 Bristol Rovers |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-09-06 |accessdate=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121025123/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7588621.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但上半場因[[肘|手肘]]脫臼離場，需要缺陣6星期<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7606776.stm |title=Posh hit with double injury blow |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-09-09 |accessdate=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107104033/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7606776.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。10月23日復出不久的麥連在4-0擊敗[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲爾德]]中取得兩個入球兼協助彼德堡在聯賽9場不敗<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7674568.stm |title=Peterborough 4-0 Huddersfield |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-10-23 |accessdate=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029155631/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7674568.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。在升上一級聯賽及受傷患困擾，麥連未能如去季般入球如拾草芥，直到11月底只有6球進賬，領隊[[达伦·弗格森|达伦·弗格森]]考慮在1月轉會窗引入較具經驗的前鋒<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7761459.stm |title=Ferguson widens striker search |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-12-02 |accessdate=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107110911/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7761459.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，心儀人選包括[[瑞奇·兰伯特|瑞奇·兰伯特]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7792670.stm |title=Fry admits Lambert interests Posh |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-12-19 |accessdate=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107110718/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7792670.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但麥連對自己的能力充滿信心<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7778220.stm |title=Mclean relaxed over striker talk |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-12-12 |accessdate=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107031557/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7778220.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。12月28日彼德堡作客與[[切尔滕汉姆足球俱乐部|車頓咸]]製造另一場大交易，最終6-3獲勝，麥連射入一球，將入球總數在新年前達到雙位的10球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7787754.stm |title=Cheltenham 3-6 Peterborough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-12-28 |accessdate=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029100545/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7787754.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。最終彼德堡沒有在轉會窗引入前鋒，仍依賴原有鋒線爭取升級。新年後麥連漸入佳景，在7場比賽有6球斬獲<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/carlisle_united/7912578.stm |title=Cumbrians winger keen to improve |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-02-26 |accessdate=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107111142/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/carlisle_united/7912578.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。聯賽煞科日主場2-2賽和[[斯温登足球俱乐部|史雲頓]]，雖然麥連射失一球[[十二碼|十二碼]]沒有取得入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8014939.stm |title=Peterborough 2-2 Swindon |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-02 |accessdate=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030022506/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8014939.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，球季結束麥連合共射入19球，包括18個聯賽入球，成為球隊次席射手<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/club_stats/default.stm |title=Club Stats:Top Scorers |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date= |accessdate=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2020-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200111161640/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/club_stats/default.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，並協助彼德堡連續兩年升級，來季升級到[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]。

2009年12月15日麥連提出書面轉會要求，並獲得球會接納<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/8413962.stm |title=Peterborough agree to Aaron Mclean transfer request |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-12-15 |accessdate=2009-12-16 |archive-date=2018-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181211094203/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/8413962.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2010年1月9日剛上任[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]的前彼德堡領隊[[达伦·弗格森|戴倫·費格遜]]據報向麥連招手<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_5850405,00.html |title=Ferguson targets McLean |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-01-09 |accessdate=2010-01-10 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308014542/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_5850405,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。麥連於3月19日在操練時不慎扭傷[[膝蓋|膝蓋]]，掃瞄證實[[韌帶|韌帶]]撕裂，需要接受[[手術|手術]]治療，因而缺席球季餘下賽事<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6047151,00.html |title=Posh ace could miss run in |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2010-03-22 |accessdate=2010-12-23 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310081438/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6047151,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2010年至2011年英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|2010/11年球季]]麥連傷癒復出，開季兩仗於聯賽擊敗[[布里斯托流浪足球俱乐部|布里斯托流浪]]及[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]淘汰[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:罗瑟勒姆; zh-hk:洛達咸;}-]]均取得入球，但在對洛達咸時右腿受傷用擔架抬離場，賽後需要接受[[核磁共振成像|磁力共振]]檢查傷勢<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_6306257,00.html |title=McLean set for MRI scan |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2010-08-11 |accessdate=2010-12-23}}</ref>，證實沒有[[骨折|骨折]]而可於下場聯賽對[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:伯恩茅斯; zh-hk:般尼茅夫;}-]]上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/8924209.stm |title=Posh's Mclean at ease with injury |publisher='''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]''' |date=2010-08-18 |accessdate=2010-12-23 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306235316/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/8924209.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。麥連繼續火熱演出，於[[聖誕節|聖誕節]]前在各項賽事合共射入14球，其轉會要求一直沒有撤銷，12月22日彼德堡班主達瑞·麦安东尼（Darragh MacAnthony）證實接納剛轉換班主的[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:赫尔城; zh-hk:侯城;}-]]的出價，麥連獲准與對方商討私人條件<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/9312976.stm |title=Peterborough's Aaron Mclean set for Hull City talks |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-22 |accessdate=2010-12-23 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307020220/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/9312976.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 侯城 ===
2010年12月30日麥連證實加盟[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|侯城]]，轉會費確實金額沒有透露，據報超過100萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，簽約三年半<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/9312976.stm |title=Hull City sign Peterborough United striker Aaron Mclean |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-30 |accessdate=2010-12-30 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307031318/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/9312976.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年1月4日，[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]從[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|侯城]]借得麥連直至球季結朿<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20912757 |title=David McGoldrick & Aaron McLean join Ipswich Town |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-01-04 |accessdate=2013-11-22 |archive-date=2015-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150306174850/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20912757 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年11月21日，[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰]]以緊急借用形式向[[英超|英超]]球會[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|侯城]]借得麥連直至2014年1月1日<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/25040827 |title=Birmingham City sign Hull City striker Aaron McLean |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-11-21 |accessdate=2013-11-22 |archive-date=2015-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150104051111/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/25040827 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
